# Hero: sage war cockpit (~10s) with selection movement.
Output ../assets/demo-war.gif
Output build/demo-war.txt
Set Width 1200
Set Height 640
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH NO_COLOR=1" Enter
Type "unset FORCE_COLOR 2>/dev/null; clear" Enter
Show
Type "sage war"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Up
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 800ms
Sleep 2s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
